==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oppositifolious
<hw>Op*pos`i*ti*fo"li*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Opposite</er>, <er>Folious</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Placed at the same node with a leaf, but separated from it by the
whole diameter of the stem; <as>as, an <ex>oppositifolious</ex>
peduncle</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Opposition</ent>⟦br⟧
